/merchant-feed.xml?*         https://nojvgfbcjgipjxpfatmm.supabase.co/functions/v1/google-shopping-feed 301!

# www -> apex: NOT handled here — Cloudflare Pages ignores full-URL _redirects rules.
# Use Cloudflare Dashboard → Rules → Redirect Rules to create a 301 for www → apex.
# lovable.app -> apex: Same — must be a Cloudflare Redirect Rule, not a _redirects entry.

